{"tid":771683,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"今日個00後話暑假工係拎經驗 我地成班笑佢老套 笑到佢喊","createTime":"2018-08-08T07:13:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-08T08:08:32.000Z","uid":1734,"like":13,"dislike":43,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5c3dc1a2baf4ea6e1d59df94e10726549291d203","tid":771683,"uid":1734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T07:13:43.000Z","msg":"今日大老細請食lunch  成班去飲茶 咁老細難得一齊食飯 一定問下我地返工返成點有咩想改善 <br />\n大家都話希望加人工啦  最好加多幾日假比我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點知個00後話我返暑期工係為左拎經驗 睇錢唔係咁重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我地當住佢面笑 仲話鳩佢on99咁 老細都忍唔住笑佢  我仲問佢減你人工比多d野你做好無咁串佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   佢當堂眼濕濕咁  最後比我地笑到喊住咁走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 飯都無食  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好心00後就唔好咁造作啦 抵比我地串<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  你地咁on9實玩死你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"592f4e02c46ee31a5cdf7cffacdc6215e46e65e5","tid":771683,"uid":1734,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T07:15:32.000Z","msg":"屌又負皮 仆街00後"},{"pid":"a7fc38157f27db9abaef2871984a3f1ffcdc8919","tid":771683,"uid":810,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T07:15:48.000Z","msg":"d00後真系冇撚腦😂"},{"pid":"08f77c2181af31039d05c189836cda7c8689aed2","tid":771683,"uid":1734,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a7fc38157f27db9abaef2871984a3f1ffcdc8919","tid":771683,"uid":810,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T07:15:48.000Z","msg":"d00後真系冇撚腦😂"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T07:16:18.000Z","msg":"真係對00後好反感 好心唔好咁on9啦"},{"pid":"ae1ba333650191d9cf7a078c321a7ed66d11d4a2","tid":771683,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit